<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَإِن شِئْت من الضَّمِير فِي <span style="color:#008000">(غَدا)</span> على قَول من جعل للاسم الْوَاحِد حَالين فَصَاعِدا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>و <span style="color:#008000">(هافيا)</span> حَال من الضَّمِير فِي <span style="color:#008000">(يُعَارض)</span> و <span style="color:#008000">(يخوت)</span> حَال من الضَّمِير فِي <span style="color:#008000">(هافيا)</span> و <span style="color:#008000">(بأذناب)</span> طرف <span style="color:#008000">(ليخوت)</span> ، وَالْبَاء بِمَعْنى فِي.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>و <span style="color:#008000">(يعسل)</span> مَعْطُوف على <span style="color:#008000">(يخوت)</span> .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢٨ - <span style="color:#008000">(فَلَمَّا لواه الْقُوت من حَيْثُ أمه ... دَعَا فأجابته نَظَائِر نحل)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#707070">[اللُّغَة]</span> : لواه: دَفعه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَأمه:</span> قَصده.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَنحل:</span> ضوامر.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَمن قَالَ:</span> قحل فَهُوَ غلط.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#707070">[الْإِعْرَاب]</span> : <span style="color:#008000">(لما)</span> ظرف زمَان لَهُ جَوَاب، وَجَوَابه <span style="color:#707070">[هُوَ]</span> الْعَامِل فِيهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَهُوَ هُنَا <span style="color:#008000">(دَعَا)</span> .<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>و <span style="color:#008000">(من)</span> تتَعَلَّق<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>